metadata.name: Hindu Goddess Durga
metadata.description:
A 1/1 NFT in honor of the annual Hindu festival Durga Puja that pays homage to the Hindu Godess Durga. 
The celebration begins on October 1 2022 and marks the victory of goddess Durga in her battle against the shape-shifting Asura, Mahishasura.

The festival epitomizes the victory of good over evil, though it is also in part a harvest festival celebrating the goddess as the motherly power behind all of life and creation
